ğŸ“Œ Very powerful for development

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âš ï¸ Common Redux Mistakes

âŒ Mutating state directly
âŒ Too many global states
âŒ Overusing Redux
âŒ Complex reducers

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

âœ” Use Redux Toolkit
âœ” Keep state normalized
âœ” Use slices
âœ” Avoid over-complication
âœ” Separate feature folders

